Go cat go Devil With The Blue Dress On ->

Devil With The Blue Dress On ->

What other band could pull this off in a 20,000 capacity shed in 1987? Hilarious!

I thought it rocked.

Desolation Row One of the best Desolation Row's I have ever heard.  A true gift.  (5 stars for the Desolation Row alone, still listening to the remainder of the show.)

Many blessings to all who have made Archive.org's Live Music Archive and its content, especially the thousands of Grateful Dead recordings, available to us all!
Great Show This is a great show, I'm really enjoying it but the whole second set is mislabeled
Awsome Show Absolute great show, but the second set is entirely mislabeled. If a show is going to run 3 disks let it, it takes a long time putting things back in order again.
Of course,I was there!  Interesting song selections.I was sitting 8th row center for this 1. Thank you tapers.Thank you @Charlie Miller.Listen loud & #dontletgo
